ReadCase
data.value: select distinct T1.NUMB from CKT_CASE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEG_ACT_CAS_RL T3 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.NUMB = T3.CAS_NUMBER) and (@lgaId = T3.LGA_ID)

data.name: ReadCaseAssignment
data.value: select top(1) REASON_CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE with(readuncommitted) where (@casNo = CAS_NO) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadLegalAction
data.value: select LEGAL_ACTION_ID, ACTION_TAKEN, STANDARD_NO, CREATED_TSTAMP from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION with(readuncommitted) where (ACTION_TAKEN = 'ORDIWO2') and (CREATED_TSTAMP between cast(@timestamp1 as datetime2) and cast(@timestamp2 as datetime2)) and (LEGAL_ACTION_ID > @legalActionId) order by LEGAL_ACTION_ID

data.name: ReadLegalActionIncomeSource
